title: Numbers Don't Lie
itunes:title: Numbers Don't Lie
description:
Dear Steve and Shirley, I’m 33 years old and single. My uncle is like a father to me and he helped my mother raise me. He is a sweetheart of a man and he loves the Lord. He’s active in his church and he will help anyone that needs him. He’s worked all of his life and he’s got a little fortune saved up. He is 58 and he has never been married, so he was anxious to settle down...............................................
